OL,3,CGarner gets WBC interim belt with St
OL,4,CMary's win over Magnesi
OL,6,FRyan Garner delighted a partisan crowd
OL,7,Fat St Mary's with victory on points
OL,8,Fover Michael Magnesi to claim the WBC
OL,9,Finterim super-featherweight title.
OL,11,FSouthampton fan Garner was straight
OL,12,Fout of the blocks against his
OL,13,Fexperienced opponent and even though
OL,14,Fthe duo traded punches, the 28-year-
OL,15,Fold achieved a lifelong goal of boxing
OL,16,Fand winning at the home of his beloved
OL,17,FSaints with scores of 119-109, 118-110
OL,18,Fand 116-112.
