OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1782065473
OL,3,CGarner gets WBC interim belt with St
OL,4,CMary's win over Magnesi
OL,6,F"Listen, if it wasn't for Southampton
OL,7,FFootball Club and all the Southampton
OL,8,Ffans, this wouldn't happen," he said
OL,9,Fafterwards.
OL,11,F"Thank you Frank Warren for making it
OL,12,Fhappen. You promised me years ago you
OL,13,Fwould and I can't thank you enough,"
OL,14,FGarner said in the ring.
OL,16,F"(Michael) doesn't stop coming, he is
OL,17,Fa machine and I had to dig deep there
OL,18,Fat some times, but I've been doing
OL,19,Fthis 18 years now and I've always said
OL,20,FI have got an engine.
