OL,3,CGarner gets WBC interim belt with St
OL,4,CMary's win over Magnesi
OL,6,F"You saw I had an engine and I am very
OL,7,Fthankful I am in the position I am. I
OL,8,Fwant to thank everyone that came out
OL,9,Fto support me. This wouldn't be
OL,10,Fpossible if it wasn't for you."
